				<q class="begin-double" qid="" from="" to="">
				</q>
				I have labored in vain;
				<end-line class="br">
				</end-line>
				<begin-line class="indent">
				</begin-line>
				I have spent my strength for nothing and vanity;
				<end-line class="br">
				</end-line>
				<begin-line
					>
				</begin-line>
				yet surely my right is with the 
				<span class="divine-name">
					Lord
				</span>
				,
				<end-line class="br">
				</end-line>
				<begin-line class="indent">
				</begin-line>
